             <p>[18r1]m iti | bhagavān āha | gṛhapate
                 tvayā etāni dātavyāni dīyatāṃ brāhmaṇāyeti | tato nāthapiṇḍadena gṛhapatinā sā
                 suvaṇṇahelā brāhmaṇāya dattāḥ bhikṣavaḥ saṃśayajātāḥ sarāji[18r2]kā ca parṣat
                 sarvvaśaṃsaya[cchettāraṃ] buddham bhagavantaṃ papracchuḥ | kasya
                 bhaga<g>%</g>van yāvad anena brāhmaṇena bhagavān vidhārito nāthapiṇḍadena ca
                 kārṣāpaṇā dattāḥ kutaś ca prabhṛti bha[18r3]gavān asmai dhārayata iti ||
                 bhagavān āha | icchatha yūyaṃ bhikṣavaḥ śro<g>%</g>tum evaṃ bhadanta tena hi
                 bhikṣavaḥ śṛṇuta sādhu ca suṣṭhu ca manasi kuruta, bhāṣiṣye bhūtapūrvaṃ bhikṣavo
                 ’tī[18r4]te ’dhvani vārāṇasīnagaryāṃ brahmadatto nāma rājā rājyaṃ kārayati
                 <g>%</g> ṛddhañ ca sphītañ ca kṣemañ ca subhikṣañ cākīrṇṇabahujanamanuṣyañ
                 ca praśāntakalikalahaḍimbaḍamarataskara ¦[18r5]rogāpagataṃ
                 śālīkṣugomahiṣīsampannam akhilam akaṇṭakam eka<g>%</g>putram iva rājyaṃ pālayati
                 | tasya jyeṣṭha<add place="inline">ḥ</add> kumāro yuvarājaḥ so pareṇa samayena
                 vasantakālasama¦[183r6]ye saṃpuṣpiteṣu pādapeṣu
